00:18:58.583 --> 00:19:00.125
You are always hasty.

00:19:00.333 --> 00:19:01.416
-Hail the Lord.
-Ms. Ara!

00:19:02.375 --> 00:19:03.208
Sir.

00:19:03.291 --> 00:19:04.708
-I am coming.
-Not coming.

00:19:05.375 --> 00:19:06.833
No, sir. Please.

00:19:07.250 --> 00:19:09.416
