01:48:02.000 --> 01:48:05.458
Please! Just give me a chance.

01:48:15.625 --> 01:48:16.458
Delhi!

01:48:16.750 --> 01:48:17.583
Delhi!

01:48:17.750 --> 01:48:18.666
Delhi!

01:48:25.458 --> 01:48:26.333
